Titolo: Mystic Ark

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Mystic Ark (ミスティックアーク, Misutikku Āku) is a 1995 role-playing video game developed by Produce! and published by Enix for the Super Famicom. The video game was only released in Japan. Mystic Ark has strong similarities to the games The 7th Saga and Brain Lord, also developed by Produce and distributed by Enix. The game was being localized for a North American release under the title 7th Saga II, but the release was cancelled.